---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="JSON Tools, Formatter, Viewer, Regex | Irwansyah Tools"
    description="JSON tools untuk formatter, viewer, regex tester, JWT decoder, Base64, dan utility developer lain yang cepat, ringan, dan gratis di browser."
    keywords="JSON, JSON tools, JSON formatter, JSON viewer, regex tester, JWT decoder, developer tools"
    canonicalPath="/json"
>
    <section
        class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-10"
    >
        <div
            class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_280px] lg:items-center"
        >
            <div>
                <p
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-teal-700"
                >
                    JSON Landing Page
                </p>
                <h1
                    class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl"
                >
                    JSON Tools, Formatter, Viewer, dan Regex Tester
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600"
                >
                    Halaman ini fokus untuk keyword JSON dan mengumpulkan tool
                    paling sering dipakai developer saat validasi, parsing,
                    beautify, debugging API response, dan inspeksi payload
                    langsung dari browser.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a
                        href="/tools/json-formatter-validator"
                        class="rounded-xl bg-teal-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-teal-700"
                    >
                        Open JSON Formatter
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="/tools/json-viewer"
                        class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100"
                    >
                        Open JSON Viewer
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <img
                src="/json-tools-hero.svg"
                alt="JSON tools dashboard untuk formatter, viewer, regex tester, dan utility developer"
                width="640"
                height="640"
                class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[280px] rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-3"
            />
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <a
            href="/tools/json-formatter-validator"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">
                JSON Formatter / Validator
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Rapikan, beautify, minify, dan validasi JSON untuk debugging API
                request dan response.
            </p>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/tools/json-viewer"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">JSON Viewer</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Lihat struktur JSON yang nested, unstringify string JSON, dan
                konversi ke XML atau CSV.
            </p>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/tools/regex-tester"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Regex Tester</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Uji regex untuk field JSON, payload API, dan validasi data
                secara interaktif.
            </p>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/tools/jwt-decoder"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">JWT Decoder</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Decode payload token JSON untuk mengecek claims, expiry, issuer,
                dan struktur auth response.
            </p>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/tools/base64-encode-decode"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">
                Base64 Encode / Decode
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Encode dan decode string yang sering muncul di konfigurasi API
                dan payload berbasis JSON.
            </p>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/tools/timestamp-converter"
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        >
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">
                Timestamp Converter
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
                Konversi timestamp log API ke waktu manusia saat mengecek event
                di JSON response atau audit trail.
            </p>
        </a>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
